User & Server

1. User --> Server

    * login/logoff
    * status

2. Server --> user

    *online / offline

3. User --> user

    * direct messages
    * broadcast messages


Commands;

    login <user> <password>
    logoff

    msg <user> text....
    i.e "msg jim Hello World" --->sent
    jim: "msg guest Hellow World" --->received

    #topic < --- chatroom/group chat
    join #topic
    leave #topic
    send: msg #topic body...
    recv: msg #topic:<login> body...